cutscene_segment_set(12, "Les Slaypool: 'What about M-Day?'");
cutscene_segment_set(13, "Professor T: 'We don't talk about that. Anyways, your universe's Kranion has grown far too powerful for you to handle--he is far stronger than even our native Kragneto.");
cutscene_segment_set(14, "'The Multisociety fears he will become a multiversal threat if not stopped in time, and you aren't well equipped to do so.'");
cutscene_segment_set(15, "King Quincy: 'Hey, I mean, why don't we let these guys take over? We could save ourselves a lot of trouble if we let them beat up Kranion for us.'", spr_cutscene_xfreaks_4,,,,, cutscene_transitions.fade);
cutscene_segment_set(16, "Tikiman: 'I agree. It would also be rude to turn down such nice gentlemen.'");
cutscene_segment_set(17, "Gambi: 'Yeah, I guess. Kranion's peeved me off enough today. Maybe I'll go do some yoga or something.'");
cutscene_segment_set(18, "Scruffy: 'Alright, you guys got yourself a deal. Yo, Slaypool! When you're done wrecking Kranion six ways from Sunday, bring back some chimichangas for us to share!'");
cutscene_segment_set(19, "Les Slaypool: 'We gotchu. One numbskull with a side of chimichangas coming right up!'", spr_cutscene_xfreaks_5,,,,, cutscene_transitions.NA);
